    <item>
      <title>马斯克在特朗普的角色已经结束，但他的影响力保持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/is-elon-musk-resigning-from-doge-trump-adviser-expected-to-step-back</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）有望退后一职，一旦担任唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的临时顾问的130天期间，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的临时顾问已经失败，但亿万富翁仍将对联邦削减成本的努力产生重大影响，并在正式离开后仍然是特朗普的认罪者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/is-elon-musk-resigning-from-doge-trump-adviser-expected-to-step-back</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:44:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的最低关税10％使寻求交易的国家更加困难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nations-seeking-to-cut-trade-deals-with-trump-face-10-hurdle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的广泛关税宣布使外国领导人竞选与总统的交易，以降低对美国出口的关税。谈判窗口可能比他们想象的要小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nations-seeking-to-cut-trade-deals-with-trump-face-10-hurdle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:00:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p损失10％以来特朗普上任，自2001年以来最糟糕的开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-second-term-brings-worst-stock-market-start-since-2001</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）就职典礼以来，美国股市下跌了10％，这标志着自2001年乔治·W·布什（George W. Bush）自2001年在Dot-Com抛售期间的新任总统以来最糟糕的开局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-second-term-brings-worst-stock-market-start-since-2001</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 15:32:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
